                    "company": "Meneer de Journalist",
                    "description": "Meneer de Journalist is a cross media company in the heart of the Netherlands. We provide our customers with publications on all possible platforms.\n\nMeneer de Journalist includes in its portfolio: Directing fully operational websites for editorial teams, written and designed newspaper spreads, documentaries, infographics, visual storytelling, and an array of journalistic background articles, reports and commentaries.\n\nClients include: Trouw, Reader's Digest, Nederlands Dagblad, Rijkswaterstaat, Koninklijke Metaalunie, Koninklijke Nederlandse Heidemaatschappij, BDU, ICGV, Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam, Wageningen Universiteit, Tibiscus University (Timi\u0219oara, Romania), and Christelijke Hogeschool Ede.\n\nAre you Interested? Please, send us an e-mail at info@meneerdejournalist.nl\n\nSince 1999 Meneer de Journalist participates in university programmes, to help the next generation of journalists to become critical and innovative entrepreneurs. \n\nIn 2014 we received a grant from the Fonds Bijzondere Journalistieke Projecten (Dutch journalism fund) to conduct research in Drone Journalism in the Netherlands.",
